{"tid":2281963,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我發現我開始有預見同未來有關嘅能力","createTime":"2020-11-11T13:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T13:50:59.000Z","uid":243854,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"54a46aa50c7fef66ae955050fbabc73822cdd059","tid":2281963,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:18:38.000Z","msg":"話說早幾日睇Youtube無啦啦彈咗條片講隻n年前嘅game<br />\n一睇完上連登就見到個post討論<br />\n尋日睇完食神，一上連登就見到有人講套嘢<br />\n今日唔知點解諗起呢幾年嘅歌星有邊個仲喺度<br />\n就諗起許廷鏗呢條友，明明之前好似成日聽到有人聽佢歌，點解而家無咗影嘅(可能係我無留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n點知一上fb就見到雲海開post講條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7apvKsB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7apvKsB.jpg&h=bed186e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果我將呢種能力訓練成功，由睇見諗起呢d小事變成一件大事，影響世界嘅事，應該會成為下一位預言大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過首先我研究到下期六合彩發咗達先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063a90de123b48791834f6620ff6cac2848b2266","tid":2281963,"uid":167007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cache.hkgolden.media/compress/http://i.imgur.com/IO0TT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcache.hkgolden.media%2Fcompress%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FIO0TT.jpg&h=9481ae54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9af4eeeb207aef6e0be4bf0109fb4f05645510d0","tid":2281963,"uid":243854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"063a90de123b48791834f6620ff6cac2848b2266","tid":2281963,"uid":167007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T13:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cache.hkgolden.media/compress